computational linguistics in a ph.d. computer science program.wthis report contains recommendations for acourse curriculum on computational linguistics in a ph.d. computer science program.  a classification of thesubject areas contained in computational linguistics is presented, and ten courses in these areas are described. a basic bibliography in computational linguistics is appended.cacm december, kuno, s.oettinger, a. g..kcomputational linguistics, mathematical linguistics,language and computer, language data processing, computational linguistics course curriculum, computationallinguistics graduate program, computational linguistics bibliography, computer science curriculum.c. . .ca jb february ,   : pm